    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning, flawless condition\u2014it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that's basically brand new and ready for an adventure, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43900.0,
